{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"9754a97f4a","title":"题送川公审土豪劣绅大会联","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"680d469568","index":0,"year":1928,"month":1,"day":null,"articleId":"9754a97f4a"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji4-1","name":"毛泽东全集第4卷(1)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji4-1.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji4-1":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"3971f4966b","type":"paragraph","text":"题送川公审土豪劣绅大会联！","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"9754a97f4a"},{"id":"e86bbe81c7","type":"paragraph","text":"（1928年1月）你当年剥削工农，好就好，利中生利：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"9754a97f4a"},{"id":"602bdf411e","type":"paragraph","text":"我今日字杀土当回，怕不怕，刀上加刀。[111928年1月5日毛泽东率领工农革命军队攻克江西遂川县城，1月24日召开成立县工农兵政府的群众大会，公审土豪劣绅郭渭坚，并处以极刑。毛泽东在会上讲了话，并为大会亲笔书写了这副对联。遂川，县名，在江西省西南部，赣江支流遂川江上游，邻接湖南省。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"9754a97f4a"},{"id":"d15dce2d45","type":"paragraph","text":"[2]土劣，土豪劣绅的缩称。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"9754a97f4a"},{"id":"d437b0f1b0","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东率领起义部队到达井冈山，极力争取、团结、改造袁文才、王佐两支武装。图为袁文才（左）、王佐。","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"9754a97f4a"},{"id":"c59a21c37a","type":"paragraph","text":"1928年2月，毛泽东率工农革命军取得井冈山斗争的第一个胜仗，攻克宁冈县城新城，打破国民党军对井冈山的第一次“进巢”。图为油画《新城大捷》毛泽东送给袁文才骑马用的裹腿。","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"9754a97f4a"},{"id":"5db3982c1e","type":"paragraph","text":"中","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"9754a97f4a"},{"id":"ef324ad569","type":"paragraph","text":"《王佐迎接工农革命军》（中国画）","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"9754a97f4a"}],"page":{"id":"8af1110dcb","publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"9754a97f4a","start":95,"end":98}}}},"__N_SSG":true}